{"identifier":{"interfaceLanguage":"swift","url":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem"},"schemaVersion":{"major":0,"minor":3,"patch":0},"metadata":{"fragments":[{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"modules":[{"name":"Components"}],"symbolKind":"struct","externalID":"s:14OUDSComponents14OUDSSwitchItemV","title":"OUDSSwitchItem","role":"symbol","roleHeading":"Structure","navigatorTitle":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"OUDSSwitchItem"}]},"kind":"symbol","abstract":[{"text":"The ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" proposes layouts to add in your views some swith components.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"If you want to use a switch with only an indicator, prefer instead ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitch","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":".","type":"text"}],"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"OUDSSwitchItem","kind":"identifier"}],"platforms":["macOS"]}]},{"kind":"mentions","mentions":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/Controls"]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"level":2,"anchor":"Layouts","type":"heading","text":"Layouts"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The component can be rendered as two different layouts:"}]},{"type":"unorderedList","items":[{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"text":"default","type":"text"}]},{"type":"text","text":": the component has a leading indicator, a label and optional helper texts, and an optional trailing decorative icon"}]}]},{"content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"strong","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"inverse"}]},{"type":"text","text":": like the "},{"type":"emphasis","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"default"}]},{"type":"text","text":" layout but with a trailing switch indicator and a leading optional decorative icon"}]}]}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Indicator-states","type":"heading","text":"Indicator states"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"The switch indicator has two available states set as a boolean property that determines whether the toggle is on or off.","type":"text"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Particular-cases","type":"heading","text":"Particular cases"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"An "},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","type":"reference","isActive":true},{"type":"text","text":" can be related to an error situation, for example troubles for a formular."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"A dedicated look and feel is implemented for that if the "},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"isError"},{"type":"text","text":" flag is risen."},{"type":"text","text":" "},{"type":"text","text":"In that case if the component displayed an icon, this icon will be replaced automatically by an error icon."}]},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"In addition, the ","type":"text"},{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem","isActive":true,"type":"reference"},{"text":" can be in read only mode, i.e. the user cannot interact with the component yet but this component must not be considered","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"as disabled.","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"type":"text","text":"The switch can be also outlined in some cases."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Accessibility-considerations","type":"heading","text":"Accessibility considerations"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Voice Over","type":"text"}],"type":"emphasis"},{"type":"text","text":" will use several elements to describe the component: if component disabled \/ read only, if error context, the label and helper texts and a custom switch trait."}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Forbidden-by-design","type":"heading","text":"Forbidden by design"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a read only component.","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both an error situation and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"type":"text","text":"The design system does not allow to have both a read only and a disabled component."}],"type":"strong"}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Code-samples","type":"heading","text":"Code samples"},{"type":"codeListing","syntax":"swift","code":["    \/\/ Supposing we have an unselected state","    @Published var isOn: Bool = false","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but in read only mode (user cannot interact yet, but not disabled).","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, isReadOnly: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, and an helper text.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, helper: \"The Beatles\")","","    \/\/ A leading switch with an additional label.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\", isOn: $isOn, additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\", helper: \"1967\")","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an additonal label, an helper text and an icon.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Lucy in the Sky with Diamonds\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   additionalLabel: \"The Beatles\",","                   helper: \"1967\",","                   isReversed: true,","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"))","","    \/\/ A trailing switch with a label, an helper text, an icon, a divider and is about an error.","    \/\/ The inverse layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   helper: \"Put your hand in mine\",","                   icon: Image(decorative: \"ic_heart\"),","                   isReversed: true,","                   isError: true,","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ If on error, add an error message can help user to understand error context","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\",","                   isOn: $isOn,","                   isError: true,","                   errorText: \"Something wrong\",","                   hasDivider: true)","","    \/\/ A leading switch with a label, but disabled.","    \/\/ The default layout will be used here.","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Rescue from this world!\", isOn: $isOn)","        .disabled(true)","","    \/\/ Never disable a read only or an error-related switch as it will crash","    \/\/ This is forbidden by design!","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isError: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error","    OUDSSwitchItem(\"Kaboom!\", isOn: $isOn, isReadyOnly: true).disabled(true) \/\/ fatal error"]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Design-documentation","type":"heading","text":"Design documentation"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"https:\/\/unified-design-system.orange.com\/472794e18\/p\/18acc0-switch","type":"reference","isActive":true}]},{"level":2,"anchor":"Themes-rendering","type":"heading","text":"Themes rendering"},{"level":3,"anchor":"Orange","type":"heading","text":"Orange"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Orange"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Orange-Business-Tools","type":"heading","text":"Orange Business Tools"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_OrangeBusinessTools"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Sosh","type":"heading","text":"Sosh"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"identifier":"component_switchItem_Sosh","type":"image"}]},{"level":3,"anchor":"Wireframe","type":"heading","text":"Wireframe"},{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Wireframe"}]},{"style":"note","name":"Version","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"1.4.0 (Figma component design version)","type":"text"}]}]},{"style":"note","name":"Since","type":"aside","content":[{"type":"paragraph","inlineContent":[{"text":"0.14.0","type":"text"}]}]}]}],"relationshipsSections":[{"type":"conformsTo","kind":"relationships","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/7SwiftUI4ViewP"],"title":"Conforms To"}],"sections":[],"topicSections":[{"generated":true,"anchor":"Initializers","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/init(_:isOn:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:)"],"title":"Initializers"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Instance-Properties","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body"],"title":"Instance Properties"},{"generated":true,"anchor":"Default-Implementations","identifiers":["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations","doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/View-Implementations"],"title":"Default Implementations"}],"hierarchy":{"paths":[["doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents"]]},"variants":[{"traits":[{"interfaceLanguage":"swift"}],"paths":["\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem"]}],"references":{"component_switchItem_Sosh":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_switchItem_Sosh.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Sosh","alt":"A switch item component in light and dark mode with Sosh theme"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s8SendableP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s8SendableP","title":"Swift.Sendable"},"component_switchItem_Orange":{"variants":[{"url":"\/images\/OUDSComponents\/component_switchItem_Orange.png","traits":["1x","light"]}],"type":"image","identifier":"component_switchItem_Orange","alt":"A switch item component in light and dark mode with Orange theme"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSwitchItem/body":{"identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OUDSComponents\/OUDSSwitchItem\/body","role":"symbol","fragments":[{"kind":"keyword","text":"var"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"kind":"identifier","text":"body"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"keyword","text":"some"},{"kind":"text","text":" "},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP","kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"View"}],"abstract":[],"url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem\/body","title":"body","type":"topic","kind":"symbol"},"doc://OUDSComponents/s16SendableMetatypeP":{"type":"unresolvable","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/s16SendableMetatypeP","title":"Swift.SendableMetatype"},"doc://OUDSComponents/documentation/OUDSComponents/OUDSSwitchItem/init(_:isOn:helper:icon:flipIcon:isReversed:isError:errorText:isReadOnly:hasDivider:)":{"type":"topic","url":"\/documentation\/oudscomponents\/oudsswitchitem\/init(_:ison:helper:icon:flipicon:isreversed:iserror:errortext:isreadonly:hasdivider:)","role":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/OUDSComponents\/documentation\/OU